{"tid":2278304,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"萬人上街 泰警水炮射示威者","createTime":"2020-11-09T05:13:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T05:15:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7b1f18c43a2330c3702b3bed4507455a226641f9","tid":2278304,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T05:13:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201109/VIJX2R5XYBEPJCI445JI2NOMHA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201109%2FVIJX2R5XYBEPJCI445JI2NOMHA%2F&d=FEHxtXJUwAnPMx50BANU%2BZugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=53a7082a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201109%2FVIJX2R5XYBEPJCI445JI2NOMHA%2F&h=2b3cdd41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201109/VIJX2R5XYBEPJCI445JI2NOMHA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n萬人上街 泰警水炮射示威者<br />\n<br />\n泰國要求總理巴育下台及改革王室的示威持續，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n約一萬名民眾昨日在民主紀念碑舉行集會，曼谷警方部署9,000警力戒備，示威開始前亦警告示威者要遠離大皇宮至少150米，若無視警告將面臨法律訴訟，並在大皇宮外部署兩輛巴士阻擋示威者去路。<br />\n<br />\n有居泰英國人在Twitter分享照片，指示威者黃昏左右成功駛走其中一輛巴士，但正要移走鐵絲網路障時，被警方用水炮射中。有人情緒激動無懼水炮，繼續剪開鐵絲網路障，另一批示威者則跟警員及大皇宮保安員對峙。警員一度用擴音器指射水炮是「誤會」並道歉，但其後有警方指揮官宣佈，發射水炮是警告。入夜後示威者繼續留守民主紀念碑和大皇宮一帶，部份人將裝有寫給泰王哇集拉隆功、要求改革王室信件的流動郵箱，拖到警員和保安前。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/152ptSWk3dcgA33H0xMSYIWTKm8=/1771x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NEEXGCE2JZH4DBRDOQFOMXPAUI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F152ptSWk3dcgA33H0xMSYIWTKm8%3D%2F1771x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNEEXGCE2JZH4DBRDOQFOMXPAUI.jpg&h=3a386230&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■泰國警方向示威者發射水炮作警告。法新社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n促泰王與示威者對話<br />\n<br />\n昨日較早時，有示威領袖呼籲泰王和示威者對話，人權律師阿農在fb寫道：「我們希望您徹底改變自己行為，成為所有人的國王，我希望陛下會敞開心扉，與我們對話，共同解決危機」。<br />\n<br />\n法新社"},{"pid":"8940abf3dc4fc3a440bdea327f216e9487604283","tid":2278304,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T05:15:27.000Z","msg":"Up"}]}